{"tid":310624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵涌計劃建650公屋單位","createTime":"2017-07-06T03:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T08:27:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a256982dc4884cc33d6bd0e7cc8af99211d040c","tid":310624,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:16:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20080569&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20080569%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170706&d=FkitTLLBWokSQtQr7gwk%2FJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=96df69ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20080569%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170706&h=efd0bf3f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20080569&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170706</a><br />\n<br />\n葵涌計劃建650公屋單位<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n政府擬在葵涌新葵街地盤建公屋。<br />\n區議會文件圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府擬覓地建屋，最新計劃將葵涌新葵街地盤改劃為住宅用途，料可提供650個公屋單位，容納約1,600人居住。預計2019年動工，2023年完工。<br />\n<br />\n可容納1,600人<br />\n<br />\n該地盤位處葵涌道、大連排道和新葵街交界，毗鄰下葵涌村，是2014年政府介紹葵青區13幅房屋用地之一。區議會文件顯示，地盤總面積約0.5公頃，現為政府土地，包括路政署高速鐵路的臨時工地、渠務署的維修站和臨時工地等。當局建議把上述地盤涵蓋的「政府、機構或社區」和「鄉村式發展」用地，一併改劃為「住宅（甲類）2」用地作公屋發展，屆時除了渠務署維修站外，路政署和渠務署工地將停用及遷出。<br />\n此計劃的住用地積比率/非住用地積比率為6倍/9.5倍，最高建築物高度為130米，擬建單位數目約650個，預計可容納約1,600人居住。建議地盤綠化率不少於面積的20%，並會有綠化休憩、兒童及長者康樂設施，而建議零售設施約250平方米。計劃打算提供一間長者日間護理中心及幼兒中心，亦會興建行人天橋和升降機塔，連接前葵涌警察宿舍公營房屋項目及麗祖路公營房屋項目。<br />\n■記者袁楚雙"},{"pid":"bd10c7c06ce1757ccf3ebcded8120a6a246f7289","tid":310624,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170706/large/a0606a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170706%2Flarge%2Fa0606a.gif&h=8dc3e82a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府擬在葵涌新葵街地盤建公屋。<br />\n區議會文件圖片"},{"pid":"4479cbb38bd80a7276653d49dc22b88d9a78b307","tid":310624,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:19:26.000Z","msg":"一日150人"},{"pid":"fe3862e6194674438d6e2948a9b1bd545be91165","tid":310624,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:19:39.000Z","msg":"又多一個蝗蝻蟲穴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d1d0e32d6b27f448dabf9b18dcba06ca355c20","tid":310624,"uid":63482,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:21:13.000Z","msg":"蝗加蝻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n變陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c70275c265fb16471ab6ebd52d8a2057547d8b3","tid":310624,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:26:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6983571eb20715513d137cc3a6b58f065eb43f9f","tid":310624,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"大連排...而家已經係沙漠級"},{"pid":"37c57b4c8937ec6150660fab4806863112de770a","tid":310624,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"都要起啦，有地就起，失業呀屌"},{"pid":"154c193ae0f09b41b6654961cd2d0126720e06ba","tid":310624,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"個位置幾差下<br />\n<br />\n俾山，工廠區，黑警，公路夾住<br />\n<br />\n入到去住應該周身唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9462816ae682560782df5aa41d4c6e7d66186d","tid":310624,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個位置幾差下<br />\n<br />\n俾山，工廠區，黑警，公路夾住<br />\n<br />\n入到去住應該周身唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有葵涌道（北段）嘅車輛噪音、葵涌道（北行）右轉大連排道嘅擠塞問題，<br />\n至今未有解決方案。"},{"pid":"43243bd9e1103c3d417c4b2cc037806510f86a29","tid":310624,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:36:51.000Z","msg":"落地鐵站要搭巴士"},{"pid":"75b9ecb5314b8758769adf110b0f0816ba5b1325","tid":310624,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:37:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日150個單程證<br />\n夠緩衝一星期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n非常好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aafaebb4533d146ba982b82f071da5f03d8aaf7","tid":310624,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一日150人</blockquote><br />\n頂到10日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84df02d2871aab04834934e94b76b0ba6ebdf413","tid":310624,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落地鐵站要搭巴士</blockquote><br />\n唔使，只需行路橫過葵涌道，過埋葵涌警署，就係葵芳站巴士總站及地鐵站。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06eb5c80207b0642a30e3e7dc4c64f9001c36418","tid":310624,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>落地鐵站要搭巴士</blockquote><br />\n唔使，只需行路橫過葵涌道，過埋葵涌警署，就係葵芳站巴士總站及地鐵站。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個位算係方便<br />\n不過一定好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d4f68abf96b5364b0a729017cbb7ced4d8fe26","tid":310624,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>落地鐵站要搭巴士</blockquote><br />\n唔使，只需行路橫過葵涌道，過埋葵涌警署，就係葵芳站巴士總站及地鐵站。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個位算係方便<br />\n不過一定好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔怕嘈，最多全日關窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8486cf3768fb8d2c51241c2f963047049afa2f","tid":310624,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>落地鐵站要搭巴士</blockquote><br />\n唔使，只需行路橫過葵涌道，過埋葵涌警署，就係葵芳站巴士總站及地鐵站。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個位算係方便<br />\n不過一定好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔怕嘈，最多全日關窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n左邊煮咖喱，右邊大媽舞"},{"pid":"efd923ec4e9984864a28bfdff5d812567ad8a0d9","tid":310624,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>落地鐵站要搭巴士</blockquote><br />\n唔使，只需行路橫過葵涌道，過埋葵涌警署，就係葵芳站巴士總站及地鐵站。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個位算係方便<br />\n不過一定好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔怕嘈，最多全日關窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記得南葵涌公共圖書館，有本2004年一間大學製作，<br />\n有關改善葵芳市中心運輸與設施嘅研究報告。<br />\n當中新葵街起公屋單位果塊地，當年研究報告係建議：<span style=\"color: violet;\">闢作社區及休憩設施</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a64288339827e3882079464b263a0bfc8420ca7","tid":310624,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>落地鐵站要搭巴士</blockquote><br />\n唔使，只需行路橫過葵涌道，過埋葵涌警署，就係葵芳站巴士總站及地鐵站。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個位算係方便<br />\n不過一定好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多成堆廢老住果度，日日要橫跨葵涌道<br />\n<br />\n唔知一年會多幾多交通部事故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c0dcbf66bdca8772110d18e869c4cba75ebfe4","tid":310624,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:04:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蝗置居</span>"},{"pid":"f5e458355e6f88a3f55a26a777596da4de7a672d","tid":310624,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:59:01.000Z","msg":"拆晒犬舍匪犬唔嘈咩？"},{"pid":"b7f760956be174183d7cc267b87672a678d7d4c1","tid":310624,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:13:15.000Z","msg":"公路噪音，仲要咁近工廠區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0224a4219fb7714030546f84a977812fa82bbb7f","tid":310624,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:19:30.000Z","msg":"仲嫌唔夠逼呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e086e404a5b6fed8196a8b85c3eb78ca1cded6","tid":310624,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:56:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公路噪音，仲要咁近工廠區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗擔心，你唔會有份住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd83ec414852d26215e2e4856d53c59fdc2079a5","tid":310624,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公路噪音，仲要咁近工廠區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家仲鬼有工業活動咩 轉曬做倉同寫字樓啦"}]}